  "title": "Sales Manager (Audio Visual/Technology)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Develop and execute strategic sales plans to drive revenue growth within the assigned territory.</li><li>Monitor industry trends, competitor movements, and customer demands to fine-tune sales strategies.</li><li>Cultivate strong client relationships while actively seeking new business opportunities in the <strong>AV sector.</strong></li><li>Provide consistent follow-ups and high-quality customer service to enhance client retention and satisfaction.</li><li>Track sales performance by preparing detailed forecasts and reports, ensuring alignment with business goals.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma and above</li><li>At least 4 years of sales experience in the <strong>Audio Visual/Technology Industry.</strong></li><li>Excellent communication and negotiation skills to engage effectively with stakeholders.</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills to assess market opportunities and challenges.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br />Registration: R21100996</p>",
